    <div class="full-title with-title-branding">
      <div class="title-branding"><a href="/taxonomy/term/868"><img src="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/sites/bfi.org.uk/files/styles/16x9_small/public/sight-and-sound-logo-280x69.png?itok=AEegRSbk" alt="" /></a></div>
  
  <h1>
          Sight & Sound’s top five film books    
    
      </h1>

  
  
        <div class="copy">
              <div class="intro"><p>Which are the best five books about film ever written? This was the question Sight <span class="amp">&amp;</span> Sound asked 51 leading critics and writers – and a clear-cut top five emerged…</p>
<p>☞ <a href="/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/polls-surveys/film-book-poll/introduction">Read our editor’s introduction</a><br />
	☞ <a href="/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/polls-surveys/film-book-poll/complete">See the full poll</a></p>
<p>Sight <span class="amp">&amp;</span> Sound reviews the latest film books every month. </p>
</div>
            
      
              <p class="author-data">
          <span class="date">Updated: <time datetime="2020-05-08">8 May 2020</time></span>        </p>
      
      
          </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="block">
      
  <div class="content">
    
