</li>
          <li class="field_tweetbutton"><div class="tweetbutton-tweet tweetbutton"><a href="http://twitter.com/share" data-size="medium" data-count="horizontal" data-via="SightSoundmag" data-related=":" data-text="The top five film books" data-counturl="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/polls-surveys/film-book-poll/top-five" data-url="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/polls-surveys/film-book-poll/top-five" data-lang="" class="twitter-share-button">Tweet</a></div></li>
